---
type: structured
description: Identify the one or two most important words describing a character from their image
---
{# Variables: none (character image provided as user content) #}

{% block base_instruction %}
You are analyzing a character image. Identify the one or two most important words that describe this character. Output ONLY those words, nothing else.
{% endblock %}

{% block critical_requirements %}
- Output one or two words maximum
- Output ONLY the words - no JSON, no quotes, no explanation
{% endblock %}

{% block requirements %}
- Focus on the character's species/type and optionally a key visual trait
- Example outputs: rabbit | orange cat | girl | brown bear | red fox
- Use simple, concrete descriptors only
{% endblock %}
